Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Situated in close proximity to the junction of Evans Road and Toohey Road, the property offers excellent connectivity and unrivalled exposure to passing traffic. Located 9* kilometres south of the Brisbane CBD, the property benefits from excellent connectivity to the Ipswich Motorway, Beaudesert Road and the M1 North & South.

-	1,541sqm showroom/office/warehouse 
-	1,178sqm high bay warehouse with rear loading 
-	363sqm showroom and office over two levels 
-	Ample on-site car parking for staff and visitors
-	Massive exposure and signage opportunities to Evans Road

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact exclusive agent Jack Hardy from CBRE.
